Code Attribution Notice:
This software includes and modifies code from the HSP calculation methods published in:
Mathieu, D. "Pencil and Paper Estimation of Hansen Solubility Parameters". ACS Omega, 2018, 3 (12)
The original implementation has been:

Modified to integrate GCVOL calculation methods
Extended with additional functionality
Restructured for improved usability
Used under academic fair use for research purposes

If you use this code in your research, please cite both:

The original paper (Mathieu, 2018)
The GCVOL method paper (Ihmels & Gmehling, 2002)
